      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a vehicle to tinker with? This car is in poor condition and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone handy! It's priced to sell and ready for a dedicated owner who sees the potential in a true fixer-upper!",
