    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering in pristine, flawless condition. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a legacy of uncompromising care, ensuring a driving experience that is as distinguished as it is refined. For the connoisseur who accepts nothing less than perfection, this offering stands without peer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
